{"tid":2516150,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"檢測站繼續人龍　外傭：對政府未要求其他市民進行強制檢測感奇怪","createTime":"2021-05-04T12:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T12:52:15.000Z","uid":261647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f8847645e24652a76eb08391cd5eb806cb86486e","tid":2516150,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T12:47:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/truthmediahk/posts/3973336069400551\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftruthmediahk%2Fposts%2F3973336069400551&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK4Vo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=b47d479b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/truthmediahk/posts/3973336069400551</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：TMHK<br />\n<br />\n【多區檢測站繼續出現人龍 外傭：對政府未要求其他市民進行強制檢測感奇怪】<br />\n<br />\n政府週五宣布要求全港外傭在本月九日或之前接受新冠病毒強制檢測，繼昨天後，多區檢測站今日繼續出現人龍。<br />\n<br />\n如昨天一樣，有未預先預約的外傭清晨已到檢測站外排隊，認為做檢測可以保障自己，惟認為外傭與普通市民受感染機率差不多，對政府只要求外傭強制檢測的決定感到奇怪。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://wp.me/p5YkFQ-qji\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwp.me%2Fp5YkFQ-qji&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK4Vo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=a474e2b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wp.me/p5YkFQ-qji</a><br />\n<br />\n攝：Gordon Choi<br />\n文：Kevin Li<br />\n#TMHK20210502"},{"pid":"000fbb5879b8ec170af793ad2d8ff7c196f867bb","tid":2516150,"uid":8332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T12:52:15.000Z","msg":"放假聚埋一齊，容易同外國人有親密關係，但係又同僱主住埋一齊，所以咪強檢"}]}